    "name": "Gales of Nayeli",
    "steam_appid": 1878490,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/2590869187cd71cb06618e396bf5ab70.avif?t=1762389758\" width=514 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gales of Nayeli is a grid-based Strategy RPG coming to PC in 2025. In this enthralling SRPG adventure, you will meet and customize your party from a cast of over 35 varied and unique characters.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic SRPGs and JRPGs, Gales of Nayeli features an interactive campaign where your choices have lasting consequences throughout the entire game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/a418d71ce7fd1b60ebd53757417f4f4c.apng?t=1762389758\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/a418d71ce7fd1b60ebd53757417f4f4c.poster.avif?t=1762389758\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=117 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/f998d3af9aad8905ba6ad3a07e7e2161.avif?t=1762389758\" width=514 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/efbde68b4d5452698408f0f851695541.poster.avif?t=1762389758\" width=600 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/efbde68b4d5452698408f0f851695541.webm?t=1762389758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/efbde68b4d5452698408f0f851695541.mp4?t=1762389758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wave of darkness looms over Iuven. Otherwise friendly woodland spirits and critters are going berserk. Pirates and brigands are threatening Solance. A dark omen looms over the sands of Nareh, following the eradication of the Naga.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something must be done.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nayeli, chieftain-to-be of the Gaowaga, departs on her journey, uniting unlikely allies in hopes of bringing order back to the land of Iuven.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will it be enough to stop the imminent threat looming over Iuven? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/a6bf9036522bab05825838836f7da000.apng?t=1762389758\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/a6bf9036522bab05825838836f7da000.poster.avif?t=1762389758\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=117 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/b47f52d54aa041251a61cb837d6917be.avif?t=1762389758\" width=514 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/b84d9c0b4add91d539730c8f45d40f2c.poster.avif?t=1762389758\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/b84d9c0b4add91d539730c8f45d40f2c.webm?t=1762389758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/b84d9c0b4add91d539730c8f45d40f2c.mp4?t=1762389758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, every character’s abilities in battle will increase in diverse ways. These increases aren’t simply reflected in their statistics. Entirely new abilities and movement options can be learned through experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will also have a meaningful role to play in every character’s growth. The actions you take throughout the story will grant new skills to characters, both through story choices you make and through the use of skill scrolls, which can teach a skill to any character of your choice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/6ee78f1ecaeecacb7acdef685965d004.apng?t=1762389758\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878490/extras/6ee78f1ecaeecacb7acdef685965d004.poster.avif?t=1762389758\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=117 /></picture></span></p>",
